    [
      [
        "The event kept going on, but for me, the people I had met were more than enough."
      ],
      [
        "I decide to go up to Helpie to tell them about my prospect list. "
      ],
      [
        "[tn], you’re back! I sensed your inputs..."
      ],
      [
        "and you really didn’t like anyone! Is this correct?!"
      ],
      [
        "Yeah…"
      ],
      [
        "to be honest helpie, I didn’t like anyone in here."
      ],
      [
        "And also, don’t you think dating someone just because I talked for a moment with them is kinda rushed?"
      ],
      [
        "what happened to a good ‘ol slowburn romance?"
      ],
      [
        "O-oh… I guess you’re right [tn]..."
      ],
      [
        "so…"
      ],
      [
        "what do you want to do now?"
      ],
      [
        "I think for a while until I remember that there’s this movie in the cinema that I’ve been meaning to see."
      ],
      [
        "How about we go see that movie I talked to you about last Sunday?"
      ],
      [
        "My treat! As always, lol."
      ],
      [
        "Of course [tn]! I’ll check for the best routes to arrive early to the next function."
      ],
      [
        "Searching for best results."
      ],
      [
        "We step out of that corny cafeteria and I look up to the sky."
      ],
      [
        "The sun shines beautifully as it gently brushes my skin."
      ],
      [
        " I look at Helpie and they show me the best route to follow."
      ],
      [
        "Even if I didn’t find my true love in there, I know that I eventually will."
      ],
      [
        "But this time, I don’t want to rush things with quick dates."
      ],
      [
        "Until that time comes, I’ve got myself."
      ],
      [
        "And It’s more than enough."
      ]
